    • search

      public ArrayList<String> search(String text)
      Search a text file in the annotation
    • Search if it is a position and go
    • Search if it is contains in getChromosome().getAllElements().keySet()
    • Search if it is contains in gene.getName()
      All the search are case insensitive using text.toUpperCase();
      • Parameters:
      text -
      Returns:
